{"tid":87652,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我的蛇王日記","createTime":"2017-01-20T04:08:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-20T04:16:43.000Z","uid":77822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8aac2d7531293d5f231950243b7e3f1dd3c85760","tid":87652,"uid":77822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T04:08:30.000Z","msg":"出門口遲大到, 索性請假SL 一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求其上架巴士, 開始一日既蛇王之旅<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/20/114651_00f2830c672683a5bd211c3eb234caed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F20%2F114651_00f2830c672683a5bd211c3eb234caed.jpg&h=801e3195&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今日個天好清<br />\n<br />\n一路沿住條馬路行<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/20/114810_04ff6805f6532f27ad865182af49637e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F20%2F114810_04ff6805f6532f27ad865182af49637e.jpg&h=4471f08e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTXBuztnT6XTJzp8jPoDkyq5UgcuHL75FizffvPSBfC4J?filename=y7t62Di.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy7t62Di.jpg&h=acc293e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行行下, 行左入跑馬地<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/20/114903_3c4d165be79118ea966f700f56a18820.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F20%2F114903_3c4d165be79118ea966f700f56a18820.jpg&h=cead7e4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n扮工既人最岩梗係去公園j 吓啲唔洗返工既人妻<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmV5Gm6hGctJ4qWHYqn9V9KpJmrqRmgfjFYu5MK2HcJQux?filename=y18Ohsq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy18Ohsq.jpg&h=f7194b3e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/20/115222_03bc16b74e6d7fd256e1d4b1643df345.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F20%2F115222_03bc16b74e6d7fd256e1d4b1643df345.jpg&h=da4607da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n索人妻見唔到, 得返堆賓賓同外國bb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/20/115411_7d66f4734fe4f1b7df19c1332036af6d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F20%2F115411_7d66f4734fe4f1b7df19c1332036af6d.jpg&h=5dd4d36e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/20/115413_65fa9eb95695c24520f5a11b0e315e5d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F20%2F115413_65fa9eb95695c24520f5a11b0e315e5d.jpg&h=736debf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n見到個草地好靚, 好多人係入面跑步<br />\n問下實Q 哥哥, 原來係新月公園入去<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWQKLFGYJehmB61zTym7zYQpPGuaz4JZYuqyxj6AwaZi1?filename=ss32F79.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fss32F79.jpg&h=9449b68f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbdHsF9TpdQew3JXAvwu2Uibg2mYbSUFw2m6Mn8P1oxEh?filename=4046heK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4046heK.jpg&h=977e40a8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/20/115635_e4b06d8d437b525f52809992ef48fa7d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F20%2F115635_e4b06d8d437b525f52809992ef48fa7d.jpg&h=e021620f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n搵到間屋仔, 沿樓梯向下行, 過條隧道就到<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/20/115730_d000cdfe08370f9a754929b9698c4c89.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F20%2F115730_d000cdfe08370f9a754929b9698c4c89.jpg&h=e03963b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYKY1KhCACC83BZXytFu4zq7n3H4zRBck1YjDACBAff6R?filename=mmsL621.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmmsL621.jpg&h=848d606e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最期待既畫面出現了, 一入到去, 門口已經有個操到好fit 既鬼妹係度做運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTrzoNYq7w7r8yUsdBWL1Mo1AvkF8mqZ9CNT8p7kNoALo?filename=2B9ih5c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2B9ih5c.jpg&h=983cd248&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/20/115951_f82ff5c2d289bfd299b323924f028a78.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F20%2F115951_f82ff5c2d289bfd299b323924f028a78.jpg&h=d21e54ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好多人就咁坐左係草地晒太陽<br />\n<br />\n我都唔輸蝕, 即刻9秒9 衝去草地霸個位晒住太陽訓返教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPDuz98D49h3PWRDZSUziKKJHRGLEdSapyWWDenSFbkdp?filename=R2ujpR6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR2ujpR6.jpg&h=13236d46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一次出post, 講到1999咁, 希望大家多多包涵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44a25c62c325ae906f06e89edb7234db6a687003","tid":87652,"uid":38293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T04:09:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"769f39b9c70fa57b34c20203e4c50449795e12f6","tid":87652,"uid":35712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T04:10:30.000Z","msg":"夠鐘啦去幼稚園門口睇放學啦"},{"pid":"56788727bb4d3f12843203da18774769f885702b","tid":87652,"uid":42009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T04:11:15.000Z","msg":"巴打住跑馬地？"},{"pid":"f34b370eb9c375c7f626914ddb0bbce0935a97f1","tid":87652,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T04:16:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}